    <h2 id='sales-associate'>Sales Associate Intern</h2>
      <h3>About the role</h3>
      <p>You will report directly to the Wholesale Manager and support the wholesale team by investigating new and potential clients, managing existing client database, and aiding in fulfillment.</p>
      <p>Responsibilities are:</p>
      <ul>
