        <li>Conducts research for brand and promotional opportunities.</li>
        <li>Maintains CRM</li>
        <li>Aids in shipping samples by tracking deliveries and notifying managers of progression and status.</li>
        <li>Creates product line sheets alongside creative team for the use of wholesale clients and customers.</li>
        <li>Communicates between operation and production teams to complete fulfillment requirements. </li>
        <li>Updates managers by consolidating, analyzing, and forwarding daily action summaries.</li>
        <li>Well-developed skills in prioritizing, organization, decision-making, time management, and verbal/written communication skills.</li>
